-300x205.jpg.webp 300w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate21-768x524.jpg.webp 768w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate21-150x102.jpg.webp 150w\" data-lazyloaded=\"1\" data-src=\"https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate21.jpg.webp\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\" data-was-processed=\"true\" />\r\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Tấm Laminate vân gỗ sồi – ảnh internet</em></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h3><span id=\"Tam-Laminate-van-go-nguyen-ban-8211-su-sang-tao-la-can-thiet\">Tấm Laminate vân gỗ nguyên bản – sự sáng tạo là cần thiết</span></h3>\r\nNhững bề mặt vân gỗ sồi, gỗ óc chó tự nhiên dù đẹp nhưng lại bị hạn chế về hình thức. Đây cũng chính là điều mà gỗ tự nhiên không thể sánh được so với gỗ công nghiệp.\r\n<div id=\"attachment_157214\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-157214 litespeed-loaded lazy-load-active\" src=\"https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate25.jpg.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\" srcset=\"https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate25.jpg.webp 880w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate25-150x150.jpg.webp 150w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate25-300x300.jpg.webp 300w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate25-768x768.jpg.webp 768w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate25-100x100.jpg.webp 100w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate25-190x190.jpg.webp 190w\" alt=\"Ứng dụng tấm Laminate trong thiết kế- ảnh internet\" width=\"880\" height=\"880\" data-srcset=\"https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate25.jpg.webp 880w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate25-150x150.jpg.webp 150w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate25-300x300.jpg.webp 300w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate25-768x768.jpg.webp 768w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate25-100x100.jpg.webp 100w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate25-190x190.jpg.webp 190w\" data-lazyloaded=\"1\" data-src=\"https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate25.jpg.webp\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\" data-was-processed=\"true\" />\r\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Ứng dụng tấm Laminate trong thiết kế- ảnh internet</em></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nVới sự sáng tạo vô hạn của các nhà thiết kế bề mặt, vân sồi và óc chó đã được biến hóa để luôn trở nên mới mẻ hơn, phù hợp với xu hướng và thị hiếu người sử dụng.\r\n<div id=\"attachment_157203\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-157203 litespeed-loaded lazy-load-active\" src=\"https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate12.jpg.webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\" srcset=\"https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate12.jpg.webp 880w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate12-150x150.jpg.webp 150w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate12-300x300.jpg.webp 300w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate12-768x768.jpg.webp 768w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate12-100x100.jpg.webp 100w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate12-190x190.jpg.webp 190w\" alt=\"Tấm Laminate vân gỗ nguyên bản - ảnh internet\" width=\"880\" height=\"880\" data-srcset=\"https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate12.jpg.webp 880w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate12-150x150.jpg.webp 150w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate12-300x300.jpg.webp 300w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate12-768x768.jpg.webp 768w, https://gotrangtri.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tam-laminate12-100x100.jpg.webp 100w, h